},{"awesomeListRepo":"kdeldycke/awesome-engineering-team-management","categoryHTML":"<h2>Engineering</h2><h3>Systems Complexity</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://amzn.com/0262014866/?tag=kevideld-20\">Living with Complexity, by Donald A. Norman</a> - In which we learn that, based on <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Law_of_conservation_of_complexity\">Tesler's law of the conservation of complexity</a>, “the total complexity of a system is a constant: as you make the person's interaction simpler, the hidden complexity behind the scenes increases. Make one part of the system simpler, said Tesler, and the rest of the system gets more complex.”</li>","updatedAt":"2020-09-22T15:12:28.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"mgramin/awesome-db-tools","categoryHTML":"<h2>Migration tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prisma/migrate\">Prisma Migrate</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/prisma/migrate\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">777</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":777,\"repo\":\"prisma/migrate\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Declarative database schema migration tool that uses a declarative data modeling syntax to describe your database schema.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-09-22T12:11:05.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"AdrienTorris/awesome-blazor","categoryHTML":"<h2>Sample Projects</h2><h3>Others</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/simutaroman/BlazorWebCamApp\">Blazor Web Camera Application Example</a><a data-role=\"trackawesome